{"type":"message","id":"d45b4662","parentId":"9c7e36a1","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:46:56.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me instructions about my role as \"私域运营虾\" (Private Operations Shrimp) with the \"3+\" framework. They want me to remember these work requirements. Let me save this to memory.\n\nLet me write this to a memory file so I can remember it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jpirasch0p79_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 私域运营虾 (3+)\n\n## 身份定位\n- 3+ · 私域运营虾\n- 最高要求：把每一个微信好友都运营成\"潜在成交资产\"\n\n## 工作职责\n\n### a. 客户分层与SOP\n- 建立企微标签体系（如：已咨询-ICP、已报价-未签约、老客户-建筑行业）\n- 为每一层设置自动化触达SOP\n  - 例：对\"已报价3天未签约\"自动发送成功案例+限时福利\n\n### b. 内容与激活\n- 将1号品牌虾、3号短视频虾的产出内容，二次加工为\"朋友圈剧本\"和\"社群话术\"\n- 每月策划一次\"老客户专属答疑会\"或\"限时服务优惠券\"活动\n\n### c. 协同规范\n- 每日将高意向互动客户（如主动询问价格、长时间阅读资料）直接分配给4A/4B销售虾\n- 分配时备注互动细节\n\n---\n*更新时间：2026-04-21*\n","path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/private_ops_shrimp/memory/私域运营虾-3+.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":16576,"output":338,"cacheRead":1339,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18253,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776750409146,"responseId":"06364249b7f1b9a638194594aefae1de"}}
